Place sliced avocados in dish and pour lemon juice over to preserve color; set aside. Toast bread. Let cool. Combine lettuce, green onions, bleu cheese, shredded Cheddar cheese and dressing. Layer 1/2 of the lettuce mixture on 3 slices of toast. Next, layer 3 slices tomatoes, followed by sliced eggs. Place second slice of toast on top of eggs. Layer remaining lettuce mixture on toast, top with turkey, avocado and bacon. Place last slice of toast on top of bacon. Secure sandwiches with toothpicks, slice in quarters.